{"type":"message","id":"0c9c77be","parentId":"509e1267","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:31:33.799Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为尚书省的subagent，完成Phase 2的执行计划。让我分析当前情况：\n\n1. **当前状态**：这是一个Node.js项目（不是C#），使用Express + SQLite\n2. **任务清单**：提到AuthService.cs、UserService.cs等，但实际代码是.js文件\n3. **问题**：任务描述与实际代码不匹配\n\n我需要：\n1. 先了解项目的真实结构和安全现状\n2. 制定符合实际代码的Phase 2执行计划\n3. 识别实际存在的安全问题\n4. 创建任务跟踪文档\n\n让我继续探索项目结构，然后制定真实的执行计划。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**【尚书省·Phase 2执行报告】**\n\n臣遵旨核查，发现重大情况需呈报：\n\n## 🚨 关键发现\n\n**任务描述与实际代码不匹配**：\n- 任务提及：AuthService.cs、UserService.cs（C#文件）\n- 实际代码：Node.js + Express + SQLite（.js文件）\n\n此乃**信息错位**，臣需重新制定符合实际代码库的Phase 2执行计划。\n\n---\n\n## 一、项目现状核查"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_896ba51c268c49759277887a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-shangshu/backend/database.js"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_99a54e792ddf4f05b8dc5eb2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspace-shangshu -name \"*.js\" -o -name \"*.ts\" | xargs wc -l 2>/dev/null | tail -1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":4660,"output":307,"cacheRead":10496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15463,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774416680443}}
{"type":"message","id":"350371b8","parentId":"0c9c77be","timestamp":"2026-03-25T05:31:33.887Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_896ba51c268c49759277887a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"const sqlite3 = require('sqlite3').verbose();\nconst path = require('path');\n\nconst dbPath = path.join(__dirname, 'app.db');\n\n// 创建数据库连接\nconst db = new sqlite3.Database(dbPath, (err) => {\n  if (err) {\n    console.error('数据库连接失败:', err.message);\n  } else {\n    console.log('✅ 数据库连接成功:', dbPath);\n  }\n});\n\n// 初始化数据库表\ndb.serialize(() => {\n  // 1. 用户表\n  db.run(`\n    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users (\n      id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n      username TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n      email TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n      password_hash TEXT NOT NULL,\n      created_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n      updated_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\n    )\n  `);\n  console.log('✅ 用户表创建成功');\n\n  // 2. 角色表\n  db.run(`\n    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS roles (\n      id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n      name TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n      description TEXT,\n      created_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\n    )\n  `);\n  console.log('✅ 角色表创建成功');\n\n  // 3. 权限表\n  db.run(`\n    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS permissions (\n      id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n      name TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n      resource TEXT NOT NULL,\n      action TEXT NOT NULL,\n      description TEXT\n    )\n  `);\n  console.log('✅ 权限表创建成功');\n\n  // 4. 用户角色关联表\n  db.run(`\n    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS user_roles (\n      user_id INTEGER NOT NULL,\n      role_id INTEGER NOT NULL,\n      assigned_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n      PRIMARY KEY (user_id, role_id),\n      FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,\n      FOREIGN KEY (role_id) REFERENCES roles(id) ON DELETE CASCADE\n    )\n  `);\n  console.log('✅ 用户角色关联表创建成功');\n\n  // 5. 角色权限关联表\n  db.run(`\n    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS role_permissions (\n      role_id INTEGER NOT NULL,\n      permission_id INTEGER NOT NULL,\n      granted_at DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n      PRIMARY KEY (role_id, permission_id),\n      FOREIGN KEY (role_id) REFERENCES roles(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,\n      FOREIGN KEY (permission_id) REFERENCES permissions(id) ON DELETE CASCADE\n    )\n  `);\n  console.log('✅ 角色权限关联表创建成功');\n\n  // 初始化角色数据\n  const roles = [\n    ['admin', '系统管理员'],\n    ['user', '普通用户'],\n    ['manager', '管理者']\n  ];\n\n  const insertRole = db.prepare('INSERT OR IGNORE INTO roles (name, description) VALUES (?, ?)');\n  roles.forEach(role => insertRole.run(role));\n  insertRole.finalize();\n  console.log('✅ 初始角色数据插入成功');\n\n  // 初始化权限数据\n  const permissions = [\n    ['users:read', 'users', 'read', '查看用户'],\n    ['users:write', 'users', 'write', '编辑用户'],\n    ['users:delete', 'users', 'delete', '删除用户'],\n    ['roles:read', 'roles', 'read', '查看角色'],\n    ['roles:write', 'roles', 'write', '编辑角色']\n  ];\n\n  const insertPerm = db.prepare('INSERT OR IGNORE INTO permissions (name, resource, action, description) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)');\n  permissions.forEach(perm => insertPerm.run(perm));\n  insertPerm.finalize();\n  console.log('✅ 初始权限数据插入成功');\n});\n\nmodule.exports = db;\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774416693886}}
